+5. [P2] StickyCartBar animations cannot fire from this page state — `x.jsx` passes only static counts/totals into `StickyCartBar` and does not track previous cart size or first-item transition anywhere, so the “count bump” and “soft rise on first item” behaviors from the context cannot be triggered from the parent state. FIX: track previous cart count / first-item transitions in `x.jsx` and pass explicit animation triggers or state flags to `StickyCartBar`.
+6. [P2] Mode-switch removal toast has no local i18n fallback — `handleModeChange()` calls `t('cart.items_removed_mode_switch', { count: removed })`, but `cart.items_removed_mode_switch` is missing from `I18N_FALLBACKS`. If the backend translation is absent for the active language, `makeSafeT()` returns an empty string and the guest gets a blank toast. FIX: add `cart.items_removed_mode_switch` to `I18N_FALLBACKS` or switch this call to `tr()` with an explicit fallback string.
+
+## Summary
+Total: 6 findings (0 P0, 3 P1, 3 P2, 0 P3)

